snippet.title: codecentric AG
snippet.description:
Creating the digital future together.

At codecentric, we are passionate coders and technology nerds. We believe that real innovation starts with code, not buzzwords. Our mission is to champion excellence in software crafting by sharing knowledge and leveraging the power of IT communities. In Germany and around the globe.
